lks</span><br></h1></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1596980964958" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1596980964958" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1596980964998" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1596980964998"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 78.3672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">Get ready to break out the orange – King's Day is coming! This wildly popular holiday in the Netherlands is a day of non-stop fun, laughter, and celebration. Every year on <strong>April 27th</strong>, the Dutch people take to the streets to honour the birthday of their beloved King Willem-Alexander.</span><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><br></span><div><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">The festivities begin early in the morning, as people start setting up their stalls and blankets for the world's biggest street market. The markets are filled with all kinds of treasures – from vintage clothing to quirky souvenirs. It's the perfect place to find a one-of-a-kind memento to take home.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">One fun perk of King's Day is having a great excuse to dress up. </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">The Dutch national colour is orange</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">, because of the royal family's name:&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">the House of Orange-Nassau</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">We felt inspired&nbsp; by King's Day and wanted to share some our favourite orange products! Even if you're not a Dutchie, adding a pop of orange to your skincare or makeup can add a whole lot of fun. Let's embrace the colour orange together!</span><br><br></div></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681732001182" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1681732001182" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/218653be-9778-48a4-8d39-e27e4b612606/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/OrangeT.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="916" height="458" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="916" natural-height="458"></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1681731921397" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921397" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1681731921345" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681731921345" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921352" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1681731921352"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">1. Etude - Dear Darling Water Tint</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921395" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921395" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>Let's talk about one of our most compact, easy to use orange products. We're talking about the ray of sunshine in a little glass bottle, the Etude <strong>Dear Darling Water Tint</strong> in 'Orange Ade'!&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>This lip tint is perfect for those who love a juicy and <span style="background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">vibrant pop of colour</span> on their lips. It has a light watery texture but leaves a pigmented stain on the lips. The bright and cheerful shade Orange Ade is the perfect way to instantly perk up your day.</p><p><br></p><p>This lip tint is <span style="background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">ultra-long lasting</span>, so you can rock a gorgeous orange pout all day without worrying about touch-ups. It's the perfect lip product for King's Day, a cute date, or even just lounging at home in your PJs - because let's be real, who doesn't want to feel fabulous and fancy even when they're chilling at home?&nbsp;</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681731921306" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681731921306"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1680167576362" data-id="1680167576362"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1681731921357" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1681731921357" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="33188526882879" style="" data-current-variant="33188526882879">{% assign product = all_products['etude-house-dear-darling-water-tint'] %}{% unless product.empty?  %}{% f