ant;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">If you are looking to add some playfulness and a unique touch to your skin care routine, then a great option is the Benton <span style="font-weight: bold;">Let's Carrot Multi Oil</span>.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">Like the name suggests the main star in this product is carrots!&nbsp;</font></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">This multi oil is loaded with </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">Carrot Seed Oil and Carrot Extract</span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"> to give your skin a boost of beta-carotene, a powerful antioxidant that helps to </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">protect your skin</span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"> from damage.</span></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">When you apply this multi oil, it feels like a luxurious treat for your face. It's silky and lightweight, and it glides on like a dream. Plus, it's versatile enough to use on your face, body, and even your hair!&nbsp;</font></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">The Benton Let's Carrot Multi Oil hydrates your skin, nourishes it, and&nbsp; &nbsp;protects it from environmental stressors. Making it a great fun addtion to any skin care routine.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1680167685730" data-id="1680167685730"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1680167918202" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1680167918202" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="33188526882879" style="" data-current-variant="39274836951103">{% assign product = all_p