: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">It's the KUNDAL <span style="font-weight: bold;">Macadamia & Sugar Body Scrub</span>! This scrub comes in two scents: a fruity, floral </span><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">Cherry Blossom</span><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"> scent, and a fresh fruity citrus </span><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">Pink Grapefruit</span><span style="font-size: inherit; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; color: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"> scent. The combination of macadamia nuts and sweet sugar is this scrub smell absolutely delicious.</span><br></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">But it's not just the scent that's amazing - this body scrub is packed with nourishing ingredients like Macadamia Oil and Shea Butter that will leave your skin feeling <span style="background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">soft, smooth, and hydrated</span>. And the sugar crystals work like magic to <span style="background-color: rgb(254, 234, 220);">exfoliate</span> away any dry, dead skin cells, leaving you with a healthy, glowing complexion.</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-168016768573